I'm happy to announce a very big update to [Telescope](http://telesc.pe) [ [demo](http://telescope-demo.meteor.com/) | [GitHub](https://github.com/SachaG/Telescope) ]. 

Actually, this update is more like a refactoring, with over 80 commits that add new features and clean up the codebase. So let's see what's new.

