### Better Subscriptions

The other benefit is that you also don't need to load all your data right from the start. This means that Telescope will now only ask for the data it needs right now, which in turns means faster loading times. 

### Everybody's Invited!

Another cool new feature is an invite system. As before, admins can invite individual users from the admin dashboard, but users can now also invite each others (provided they are themselves invited and have an invite available). 

