### Getting Started

If you want to get started with Telescope, you can [try out the demo](http://telescope-demo.meteor.com/) or [check out the code on GitHub](https://github.com/SachaG/Telescope). 

Of course, if you want to know more about Meteor in general, there's also our book, [Discover Meteor](https://discovermeteor.com). It will teach you how to build a real-time app from scratch, using Telescope's little brother [Microscope](https://github.com/DiscoverMeteor/Microscope) as an example. 

It's been almost a year now since I started building Telescope, and I'm finally starting to feel like the code is solid. So I'll hope you'll give it a try, and maybe even join us on the project!